name: Winball
tagline: Simple pinball game wich can be controlled by a controller
body:
### Welcome to WinBall
WinBall is a easy to play pinball game we developed during a tutorial at the Technical University of Munich (TUM). This game can be played with a controller which can be used to control the different kind of interaction objects in the game.

### Developers and Contributors
@thomas1991te

### Support or Contact
By questions regarding this code please contact one of the above mentioned developers.
